WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:01.839
Your father was poisoned.

00:01.890 --> 00:04.960
I would say heavy doses
over a short period.

00:05.010 --> 00:08.000
Brace, what's the matter?

00:08.050 --> 00:09.240
The truth.

00:09.290 --> 00:11.880
Those bastards
at the Palace have opened

00:11.930 --> 00:15.080
a Royal Commission into
the sinking of the Influence.

00:15.130 --> 00:16.720
You are now one of us.

00:16.770 --> 00:18.640
You'll risk the life of your son?

00:18.690 --> 00:19.730
Zilpha.

00:21.330 --> 00:22.640
What have you done?

00:22.690 --> 00:23.890
I killed him.

00:28.730 --> 00:31.240
James, this powder is
not ready to be moved

00:31.290 --> 00:32.800
because it is unstable.

00:32.850 --> 00:35.120
We are leaving
because we have been betrayed.

00:35.170 --> 00:37.650
Sir Stuart just wants
you to know... it's war.

00:40.930 --> 00:42.290
The gloves are off.

00:44.010 --> 00:45.800
James, what are you doing?

00:45.850 --> 00:48.530
Go away.
I'm not fit to be near you now.

